`COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"`\n- `generateSecret()`: 32-byte random secret\n- `computeCommitment(secret)`: SHA256 hash\n- `deriveMatchPda(creator, nonce)`: seeds = [\"match\", creator, nonce.to_le_bytes()]\n\n### 4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/db.ts` (207 lines)\n**Purpose**: Typed database client for rounds and operator_events tables.\n\n**Key Types**:\n- `RoundPhase`: \"created\" | \"locked\" | \"settling\" | \"settled\" | \"expired\"\n- `OperatorEventType`: 9 types (secret_generated, tx_built, match_detected, settle_submitted, settle_confirmed, settle_failed, settle_retried, timeout_detected)\n- `Round`: Full match record with secret, commitment, result data, settle_tx, settle_attempts\n- Phase transitions: created→locked/expired, locked→settling, settling→settled (enforced unidirectionally)\n\n**Key Functions**:\n- `insertRound(params)`: Create new round\n- `updateRoundPhase(pda, newPhase, updates?)`: Transition phase with optional column updates\n- `getRoundByPda(pda)`: Single round lookup\n- `getRoundsByPhase(phase)`: Batch query by phase\n- `insertOperatorEvent(pda, eventType, payload)`: Audit log\n\n### 5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/config.ts` (57 lines)\n**Purpose**: Load and validate environment configuration.\n\n**Config Fields**:\n- `port`: HTTP listen port (default 3100)\n- `databaseUrl`: PostgreSQL connection string\n- `rpcUrl`: Solana RPC endpoint\n- `serverKeypair`: Keypair from JSON secret key bytes\n- `authClockSkewSeconds`: Signature verification tolerance (default 60)\n- `rateLimitPerWallet`: Per-wallet limit (default 10)\n- `rateLimitGlobal`: Global limit (default 100)\n- `workerPollIntervalMs`: Settlement worker poll interval (default 2000)\n\n### 6. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/index.ts` (59 lines)\n**Purpose**: Application wiring and module initialization.\n\n**Initialization Order**:\n1. Load config from environment\n2. Create DB client\n3. Create Solana connection\n4. Create Hono app\n5. Register routes:\n   - GET /health → status check\n   - /fairness/* → rate limiting middleware\n   - /fairness/* → auth middleware (Ed25519 signature verification)\n   - /fairness/coinflip → coinflip game routes\n6. Start settlement worker\n7. Listen on configured port\n\n**Architecture Summary**:\n- Modular dependency injection (db, connection, keypair passed to workers/routes)\n- Settlement worker is always-on background task, not tied to HTTP request/response cycle\n- Auth + rate-limiting applied uniformly to all fairness routes\n- Server pays zero on-chain fees (creator is fee payer)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: adb4c800e75330de3 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 40408\ntool_uses: 6\nduration_ms: 17826</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af244c03-5c35-4a31-9aaa-3171645fdb08","uuid":"4b2551e8-a634-419a-bac3-24a28d6bccbc","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the following files thoroughly to understand the settlement architecture:\n\n1. `services/backend/src/worker/settlement.ts` - the existing settlement worker poll loop\n2. `services/backend/src/tx-builder.ts` - existing transaction builder pattern\n3. `services/backend/src/fairness.ts` - COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID and PDA derivation\n4. `services/backend/src/db.ts` - DB client types and functions\n5. `services/backend/src/config.ts` - config fields\n6. `services/backend/src/index.ts` - how modules are wired together\n\nAll paths are under `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/`.\n\nFor each file, provide the FULL file content. I need every line.\n","agentId":"adb4c800e75330de3","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully read all six files. Here's the complete content summary:\n\n## File Content Summary\n\n### 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend/src/worker/settlement.ts` (135 lines)\n**Pu