{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LexjPTDJ3dVvrSLmKz3vny","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the files. Here's the complete exploration of the settle instruction:\n\n---\n\n## Settlement Instruction - Complete Reference\n\n### **settle Instruction Signature**\n```rust\npub fn settle(ctx: Context<Settle>, secret: [u8; 32]) -> Result<()>\n```\n\n**Discriminator** (IDL): `[175, 42, 185, 87, 144, 131, 102, 212]`\n\n---\n\n### **Account Structure (11 accounts, in order)**\n\n| # | Account Name | Mutability | Signer | PDA | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 0 | `caller` | ✓ mutable | ✓ signer | — | Anyone with the secret; pays for any tx fees |\n| 1 | `coinflip_match` | ✓ mutable | — | ✓ seeds: `[\"match\", creator, nonce]` | The match PDA; holds escrow; state written here |\n| 2 | `config` | — read-only | — | ✓ seeds: `[\"coinflip_config\"]` | Global config; provides treasury address |\n| 3 | `entropy` | — read-only | — | — | Raw account; first 32 bytes read as `[u8; 32]` entropy |\n| 4 | `treasury` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Fee destination (validated == `config.treasury`) |\n| 5 | `creator` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Creator wallet; receives payout if winner (validated == `match.creator`) |\n| 6 | `opponent` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Opponent wallet; receives payout if winner (validated == `match.opponent`) |\n| 7 | `creator_profile` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Creator's player profile on platform program (may not exist; CPI call handles) |\n| 8 | `opponent_profile` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Opponent's player profile on platform program (may not exist; CPI call handles) |\n| 9 | `platform_program` | — read-only | — | — | Platform program for CPI; address: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA` |\n| 10 | `system_program` | — read-only | — | — | Standard system program; address: `11111111111111111111111111111111` |\n\n---\n\n### **Instruction Argument**\n\n```rust\npub struct Settle {\n    pub secret: [u8; 32]  // The server's 32-byte secret; verified against match.commitment\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### **State Validation & Execution Flow**\n\n#### **1. Account Key Validation**\n```rust\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.treasury.key() == ctx.accounts.config.treasury, AccountMismatch);\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.creator.key() == ctx.accounts.coinflip_match.creator, AccountMismatch);\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.opponent.key() == ctx.accounts.coinflip_match.opponent, AccountMismatch);\n```\n\n#### **2. Phase Check**\n```rust\nrequire!(m.phase == PHASE_LOCKED, InvalidPhase);  // phase must be 1\n```\n\n#### **3. Commitment Verification**\n```rust\nverify_commitment(&m.commitment, &secret)  // SHA256(secret) must match m.commitment\n```\n\n#### **4. Result Derivation**\n```rust\nlet result_hash = derive_result(&secret, &entropy, &match_key, m.algorithm_ver);\nlet result_side = result_hash[0] % 2;  // 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails (modulo result_hash[0])\n\nlet winner_key = if result_side == m.creator_side {\n    m.creator\n} else {\n    m.opponent\n};\n```\n\n#### **5. Payout Calculation**\n```rust\nlet pool = m.entry_amount.checked_mul(2).unwrap();  // pool = entry_amount * 2\nlet (fee, nominal_payout) = calculate_net_payout(pool);  // 3% fee; winner gets nominal_payout\n```\n\n#### **6. State Update**\n```rust\nm.result_hash = result_hash;      // 32-byte derived hash\nm.result = result_side;            // 0 or 1\nm.winner = winner_key;             // Winner's Pubkey\nm.phase = PHASE_SETTLED;           // phase = 2\n```\n\n#### **7. Fee Transfer**\nTransfer `fee` lamports from match PDA to treasury via PDA signer.\n\n#### **8. CPI: Update Player Profiles**\nTwo CPI calls to platform program's `update_player_profile_cpi`:\n- **Creator**: `update_player_profile_cpi(..., 1, is_winner ? 1 : 0, entry_amount, is_winner ? nominal_payout : 0, 0)`\n- **Opponent**: `update_player_profile_cpi(..., 1, is_winner ? 0 : 1, entry_amount, is_winner ? nominal_payout : 0, 0)`\n\nArguments to CPI:\n1. Platform program account info\n2. Player profile account info\n3. Config account info\n4. Signer seeds: `[b\"coinflip_config\", &[config_bump]]`\n5. `matches_played`: 1\n6. `wins`: 1 if winner, 0 if loser\n7. `total_wagered`: entry_amount\n8. `total_winnings`: nominal_payout if winner, 0 if loser\n9. `game_type`: 0 (for coinflip)\n\n#### **9. Winner Payout**\n```rust\nlet winner_payout = match_info.lamports();  // All remaining lamports (nominal_payout + surplus)\n**winner_account.try_borrow_mut_lamports()? += winner_payout;\n**match_info.try_borrow_mut_lamports()? = 0;\nmatch_info.data.borrow_mut().fill(0);  // Zero the account data\n```\n\n#### **10. Event Emission**\n```rust\nemit!(MatchSettled {\n    creator,\n    opponent,\n    winner,\n    commitment: m.commitment,\n    secret,\n    entropy,\n    result_hash,\n    result_side,\n    payout_amount: winner_payout,\n    fee_amount: fee,\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CoinflipMatch State (Full Layout)**\n\n| Field | Type | Size | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `creator` | Pubkey | 32 | Match creator wallet |\n| `opponent` | Pubkey | 32 | Opponent wallet (default if not joined) |\n| `server` | Pubkey | 32 | Server key co-signing create |\n| `tier` | u8 | 1 | 0-7 |\n| `entry_amount` | u64 | 8 | Lamports per player |\n| `creator_side` | u8 | 1 | 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails |\n| `phase` | u8 | 1 | 0 = Waiting, 1 = Locked, 2 = Settled, 3 = Refunded |\n| `commitment` | [u8; 32] | 32 | SHA256(server_secret) |\n| `algorithm_ver` | u8 | 1 | Fairness algorithm version |\n| `target_slot` | u64 | 8 | Slot for entropy read |\n| `resolve_deadline` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp; after this, timeout refund available |\n| `result_hash` | [u8; 32] | 32 | Derived result (set on settle) |\n| `result` | u8 | 1 | 0 or 1 (set on settle) |\n| `winner` | Pubkey | 32 | Winner's Pubkey (set on settle) |\n| `created_at` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp |\n| `nonce` | u64 | 8 | From player profile (used in PDA seeds) |\n| `bump` | u8 | 1 | PDA bump |\n| `creator_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Mutual refund vote |\n| `opponent_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Mutual refund vote |\n| **Total** | — | **246** | 8 (discriminator) + 238 (InitSpace) |\n\n---\n\n### **Fairness Functions**\n\n#### **verify_commitment**\n```rust\npub fn verify_commitment(commitment: &[u8; 32], secret: &[u8; 32]) -> Result<()> {\n    let hash = hashv(&[secret]);\n    require!(hash.to_bytes() == *commitment, FairnessError::CommitmentMismatch);\n    Ok(())\n}\n// Computes: SHA256(secret) and compares to commitment\n```\n\n#### **derive_result**\n```rust\npub fn derive_result(\n    secret: &[u8; 32],\n    entropy: &[u8; 32],\n    game_pda: &[u8; 32],          // match PDA key as bytes\n    algo_ver: u8,\n) -> [u8; 32] {\n    hashv(&[secret, entropy, game_pda, &[algo_ver]]).to_bytes()\n}\n// Computes: SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda_key || algorithm_version)\n```\n\n#### **read_mock_entropy**\n```rust\npub fn read_mock_entropy(account: &AccountInfo) -> Result<[u8; 32]> {\n    let data = account.try_borrow_data()?;\n    require!(data.len() >= 32, FairnessError::EntropyTooShort);\n    let mut entropy = [0u8; 32];\n    entropy.copy_from_slice(&data[..32]);\n    Ok(entropy)\n}\n// Reads first 32 bytes of any account; used in tests for mock slot hash\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Key Constants**\n\n| Constant | Value | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ALGORITHM_VERSION` | 1 | Current fairness algorithm version |\n| `ENTROPY_SLOT_OFFSET` | 12 | Number of slots to wait after join before entropy readable |\n| `PHASE_LOCKED` | 1 | Match is locked and ready to settle |\n| `PHASE_SETTLED` | 2 | Match has been settled |\n\n---\n\n### **Summary: What settle Does**\n\n1. **Validates inputs**: Verifies caller has the secret, accounts match expected keys, match is in LOCKED phase\n2. **Verifies fairness**: Checks `SHA256(secret) == commitment`\n3. **Derives result**: Computes `SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda || algo_ver)`, uses `byte[0] % 2` for coin side\n4. **Determines winner**: Compares result_side to creator_side; winner gets all remaining lamports\n5. **Calculates fees**: 3% of pool goes to treasury; winner keeps nominal_payout (pool - fees)\n6. **Updates state**: Writes result_hash, result, winner, phase to match PDA\n7. **Transfers fees**: Moves fee amount from match PDA to treasury\n8. **Updates profiles**: CPI calls to platform program to record wins/losses and stats for both players\n9. **Pays winner**: Transfers all remaining match lamports to winner's wallet\n10. **Zeros account**: Clears match PDA data and lamports, closing the escrow\n\nAll done trustlessly via on-chain verification of the commitment-reveal mechanism."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a0f3b61bcc1d18759 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 49140\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 28569</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af244c03-5c35-4a31-9aaa-3171645fdb08","uuid":"022e2dc0-0caf-4950-ba93-8bcbafb70727","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the on-chain settle instruction to understand all required accounts and arguments:\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/settle.rs` - the settle instruction\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs` - CoinflipMatch state, phases, events\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/lib.rs` - the program entry point, instruction discriminators\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.json` - the IDL (focus on the `settle` instruction section)\n5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/fairness.rs` - verify_commitment, derive_result\n\nFor each file, provide the FULL content. I need to see every account in the settle instruction context and understand argument layout.\n","agentId":"a0f3b61bcc1d18759","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the files. Here's the complete exploration of the settle instruction:\n\n---\n\n## Settlement Instruction - Complete Reference\n\n### **settle Instruction Signature**\n```rust\npub fn settle(ctx: Context<Settle>, secret: [u8; 32]) -> Result<()>\n```\n\n**Discriminator** (IDL): `[175, 42, 185, 87, 144, 131, 102, 212]`\n\n---\n\n### **Account Structure (11 accounts, in order)**\n\n| # | Account Name | Mutability | Signer | PDA | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 0 | `caller` | ✓ mutable | ✓ signer | — | Anyone with the secret; pays for any tx fees |\n| 1 | `coinflip_match` | ✓ mutable | — | ✓ seeds: `[\"match\", creator, nonce]` | The match PDA; holds escrow; state written here |\n| 2 | `config` | — read-only | — | ✓ seeds: `[\"coinflip_config\"]` | Global config; provides treasury address |\n| 3 | `entropy` | — read-only | — | — | Raw account; first 32 bytes read as `[u8; 32]` entropy |\n| 4 | `treasury` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Fee destination (validated == `config.treasury`) |\n| 5 | `creator` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Creator wallet; receives payout if winner (validated == `match.creator`) |\n| 6 | `opponent` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Opponent wallet; receives payout if winner (validated == `match.opponent`) |\n| 7 | `creator_profile` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Creator's player profile on platform program (may not exist; CPI call handles) |\n| 8 | `opponent_profile` | ✓ mutable | — | — | Opponent's player profile on platform program (may not exist; CPI call handles) |\n| 9 | `platform_program` | — read-only | — | — | Platform program for CPI; address: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA` |\n| 10 | `system_program` | — read-only | — | — | Standard system program; address: `11111111111111111111111111111111` |\n\n---\n\n### **Instruction Argument**\n\n```rust\npub struct Settle {\n    pub secret: [u8; 32]  // The server's 32-byte secret; verified against match.commitment\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### **State Validation & Execution Flow**\n\n#### **1. Account Key Validation**\n```rust\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.treasury.key() == ctx.accounts.config.treasury, AccountMismatch);\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.creator.key() == ctx.accounts.coinflip_match.creator, AccountMismatch);\nrequire!(ctx.accounts.opponent.key() == ctx.accounts.coinflip_match.opponent, AccountMismatch);\n```\n\n#### **2. Phase Check**\n```rust\nrequire!(m.phase == PHASE_LOCKED, InvalidPhase);  // phase must be 1\n```\n\n#### **3. Commitment Verification**\n```rust\nverify_commitment(&m.commitment, &secret)  // SHA256(secret) must match m.commitment\n```\n\n#### **4. Result Derivation**\n```rust\nlet result_hash = derive_result(&secret, &entropy, &match_key, m.algorithm_ver);\nlet result_side = result_hash[0] % 2;  // 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails (modulo result_hash[0])\n\nlet winner_key = if result_side == m.creator_side {\n    m.creator\n} else {\n    m.opponent\n};\n```\n\n#### **5. Payout Calculation**\n```rust\nlet pool = m.entry_amount.checked_mul(2).unwrap();  // pool = entry_amount * 2\nlet (fee, nominal_payout) = calculate_net_payout(pool);  // 3% fee; winner gets nominal_payout\n```\n\n#### **6. State Update**\n```rust\nm.result_hash = result_hash;      // 32-byte derived hash\nm.result = result_side;            // 0 or 1\nm.winner = winner_key;             // Winner's Pubkey\nm.phase = PHASE_SETTLED;           // phase = 2\n```\n\n#### **7. Fee Transfer**\nTransfer `fee` lamports from match PDA to treasury via PDA signer.\n\n#### **8. CPI: Update Player Profiles**\nTwo CPI calls to platform program's `update_player_profile_cpi`:\n- **Creator**: `update_player_profile_cpi(..., 1, is_winner ? 1 : 0, entry_amount, is_winner ? nominal_payout : 0, 0)`\n- **Opponent**: `update_player_profile_cpi(..., 1, is_winner ? 0 : 1, entry_amount, is_winner ? nominal_payout : 0, 0)`\n\nArguments to CPI:\n1. Platform program account info\n2. Player profile account info\n3. Config account info\n4. Signer seeds: `[b\"coinflip_config\", &[config_bump]]`\n5. `matches_played`: 1\n6. `wins`: 1 if winner, 0 if loser\n7. `total_wagered`: entry_amount\n8. `total_winnings`: nominal_payout if winner, 0 if loser\n9. `game_type`: 0 (for coinflip)\n\n#### **9. Winner Payout**\n```rust\nlet winner_payout = match_info.lamports();  // All remaining lamports (nominal_payout + surplus)\n**winner_account.try_borrow_mut_lamports()? += winner_payout;\n**match_info.try_borrow_mut_lamports()? = 0;\nmatch_info.data.borrow_mut().fill(0);  // Zero the account data\n```\n\n#### **10. Event Emission**\n```rust\nemit!(MatchSettled {\n    creator,\n    opponent,\n    winner,\n    commitment: m.commitment,\n    secret,\n    entropy,\n    result_hash,\n    result_side,\n    payout_amount: winner_payout,\n    fee_amount: fee,\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CoinflipMatch State (Full Layout)**\n\n| Field | Type | Size | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `creator` | Pubkey | 32 | Match creator wallet |\n| `opponent` | Pubkey | 32 | Opponent wallet (default if not joined) |\n| `server` | Pubkey | 32 | Server key co-signing create |\n| `tier` | u8 | 1 | 0-7 |\n| `entry_amount` | u64 | 8 | Lamports per player |\n| `creator_side` | u8 | 1 | 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails |\n| `phase` | u8 | 1 | 0 = Waiting, 1 = Locked, 2 = Settled, 3 = Refunded |\n| `commitment` | [u8; 32] | 32 | SHA256(server_secret) |\n| `algorithm_ver` | u8 | 1 | Fairness algorithm version |\n| `target_slot` | u64 | 8 | Slot for entropy read |\n| `resolve_deadline` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp; after this, timeout refund available |\n| `result_hash` | [u8; 32] | 32 | Derived result (set on settle) |\n| `result` | u8 | 1 | 0 or 1 (set on settle) |\n| `winner` | Pubkey | 32 | Winner's Pubkey (set on settle) |\n| `created_at` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp |\n| `nonce` | u64 | 8 | From player profile (used in PDA seeds) |\n| `bump` | u8 | 1 | PDA bump |\n| `creator_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Mutual refund vote |\n| `opponent_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Mutual refund vote |\n| **Total** | — | **246** | 8 (discriminator) + 238 (InitSpace) |\n\n---\n\n### **Fairness Functions**\n\n#### **verify_commitment**\n```rust\npub fn verify_commitment(commitment: &[u8; 32], secret: &[u8; 32]) -> Result<()> {\n    let hash = hashv(&[secret]);\n    require!(hash.to_bytes() == *commitment, FairnessError::CommitmentMismatch);\n    Ok(())\n}\n// Computes: SHA256(secret) and compares to commitment\n```\n\n#### **derive_result**\n```rust\npub fn derive_result(\n    secret: &[u8; 32],\n    entropy: &[u8; 32],\n    game_pda: &[u8; 32],          // match PDA key as bytes\n    algo_ver: u8,\n) -> [u8; 32] {\n    hashv(&[secret, entropy, game_pda, &[algo_ver]]).to_bytes()\n}\n// Computes: SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda_key || algorithm_version)\n```\n\n#### **read_mock_entropy**\n```rust\npub fn read_mock_entropy(account: &AccountInfo) -> Result<[u8; 32]> {\n    let data = account.try_borrow_data()?;\n    require!(data.len() >= 32, FairnessError::EntropyTooShort);\n    let mut entropy = [0u8; 32];\n    entropy.copy_from_slice(&data[..32]);\n    Ok(entropy)\n}\n// Reads first 32 bytes of any account; used in tests for mock slot hash\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Key Constants**\n\n| Constant | Value | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ALGORITHM_VERSION` | 1 | Current fairness algorithm version |\n| `ENTROPY_SLOT_OFFSET` | 12 | Number of slots to wait after join before entropy readable |\n| `PHASE_LOCKED` | 1 | Match is locked and ready to settle |\n| `PHASE_SETTLED` | 2 | Match has been settled |\n\n---\n\n### **Summary: What settle Does**\n\n1. **Validates inputs**: Verifies caller has the secret, accounts match expected keys, match is in LOCKED phase\n2. **Verifies fairness**: Checks `SHA256(secret) == commitment`\n3. **Derives result**: Computes `SHA256(secret || entropy || match_pda || algo_ver)`, uses `byte[0] % 2` for coin side\n4. **Determines winner**: Compares result_side to creator_side; winner gets all remaining lamports\n5. **Calculates fees**: 3% of pool goes to treasury; winner keeps nominal_payout (pool - fees)\n6. **Updates state**: Writes result_hash, result, winner, phase to match PDA\n7. **Transfers fees**: Moves fee amount from match PDA to treasury\n8. **Updates profiles**: CPI calls to platform program to record wins/losses and stats for both players\n9. **Pays winner**: Transfers all remaining match lamports to winner's wallet\n10. **Zeros account**: Clears match PDA data and lamports, closing the escrow\n\nAll done trustlessly via on-chain verification of the commitment-reveal mechanism."}],"totalDurationMs":28569,"totalTokens":49140,"totalToolUseCount":5,"usage":{"input_tokens":1202,"cache_creation_input_tokens":15796,"cache_read_input_tokens":29219,"output_tokens":2923,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":15796},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
