{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DeZvJFEtjXCryMN6qZ7kDg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information needed. Let me compile the findings:\n\n## Summary of Findings\n\n### 1. CoinflipConfig Account Layout\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs`\n\n**Struct Definition**:\n```rust\n/// Global configuration for the coinflip program.\n/// PDA seeds: [b\"coinflip_config\"]\n#[account]\n#[derive(InitSpace)]\npub struct CoinflipConfig {\n    /// Admin authority (can update config).\n    pub authority: Pubkey,\n    /// Fee destination wallet.\n    pub treasury: Pubkey,\n    /// Whether the game is paused (rejects new matches).\n    pub paused: bool,\n    /// Bump seed for PDA derivation.\n    pub bump: u8,\n}\n```\n\n**Treasury Address Storage**: The treasury address is stored in the `treasury: Pubkey` field (second field in the struct).\n\n---\n\n### 2. PlayerProfile PDA Derivation\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/src/state.rs`\n\n**Struct Definition**:\n```rust\n/// Player profile tracking game stats. One per wallet.\n/// Seeds: [b\"player_profile\", wallet.as_ref()]\n#[account]\n#[derive(InitSpace)]\npub struct PlayerProfile {\n    /// The wallet this profile belongs to.\n    pub authority: Pubkey,\n    /// Total number of games played.\n    pub total_games: u64,\n    /// Total wins.\n    pub wins: u64,\n    /// Total SOL wagered (in lamports).\n    pub total_wagered: u64,\n    /// Total SOL won (in lamports).\n    pub total_won: u64,\n    /// Monotonic counter incremented each match creation (used in match PDA seeds).\n    pub match_nonce: u64,\n    /// Bump seed for PDA derivation.\n    pub bump: u8,\n}\n```\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[b\"player_profile\", wallet.as_ref()]` (wallet is the authority/owner's Pubkey)\n\n---\n\n### 3. Settle Instruction (IDL)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.json`\n\n**Instruction Definition**:\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"settle\",\n  \"discriminator\": [175, 42, 185, 87, 144, 131, 102, 212],\n  \"accounts\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"caller\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The caller submitting the settlement. Anyone can call if they have the secret.\"],\n      \"writable\": true,\n      \"signer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"coinflip_match\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The match PDA.\"],\n      \"writable\": true,\n      \"pda\": {\n        \"seeds\": [\n          {\"kind\": \"const\", \"value\": [109, 97, 116, 99, 104]},\n          {\"kind\": \"account\", \"path\": \"coinflip_match.creator\", \"account\": \"CoinflipMatch\"},\n          {\"kind\": \"account\", \"path\": \"coinflip_match.nonce\", \"account\": \"CoinflipMatch\"}\n        ]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"config\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The config PDA (for treasury address).\"],\n      \"pda\": {\n        \"seeds\": [{\"kind\": \"const\", \"value\": [99, 111, 105, 110, 102, 108, 105, 112, 95, 99, 111, 110, 102, 105, 103]}]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"entropy\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"treasury\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The treasury account to receive fees.\"],\n      \"writable\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"creator\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The creator account.\"],\n      \"writable\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"opponent\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The opponent account.\"],\n      \"writable\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"creator_profile\",\n      \"docs\": [\"Creator's player profile PDA on the platform program.\"],\n      \"writable\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"opponent_profile\",\n      \"docs\": [\"Opponent's player profile PDA on the platform program.\"],\n      \"writable\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"platform_program\",\n      \"docs\": [\"The platform program for CPI calls.\"],\n      \"address\": \"85qwC1cDpSYkB